  "markup": "\u003Cp class=\u0022p1\u0022\u003ELow back Pain is one of the most common complaints of modern man. In the civilized world, over 80% of the population will suffer lower back pain at one point in their life. Current statistics show that many of the modern approaches offer little lasting result and that more is needed on this battle front. Research is presented demonstrating how Super Pulsed Laser is breaking new ground and offering superior outcomes for not only acute but chronic back pain suffers. Adding Super Pulsed Laser to your current protocols has been shown in clinical research to be a game changer for many common lower back complaints ranging from mechanical back pain to sciatica.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg height=\u0022505\u0022 alt=\u0022November 2012 LTU Webinar\u0022 width=\u0022590\u0022 src=\u0022~/media/6C65908D79AF439FA80E0417D4B403CB.ashx\u0022 /\u003E\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
